author: gstein
msg: For the Ev1/Ev2 shim, switch over to the new change_node structure for
(process_actions): remove the ACTION_ADD and ACTION_COPY cases, as
these are no longer stored. for RESTRUCTURE_ADD cases, extract the
kind, children, copyfrom, and maybe an empty stream. set up the
need_add and need_copy flags as appropriate.
(ev2_delete_entry): in the #if'd out code, we should use *revnum for
the base_revision rather than the parameter
(ev2_add_directory): set the KIND member in the change structure.
remove the code related to the old action structures.
(ev2_add_file): set the KIND member in the change structure. remove
the code related to the old action structures.
